{"tid":2006584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"是日主角 ： 郭榮鏗","createTime":"2020-05-08T01:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T02:20:10.000Z","uid":55456,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b7e494c51a1933d53fd4f3fae777aba78271d0c8","tid":2006584,"uid":55456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T01:18:11.000Z","msg":"未知發生咩事既可以睇下呢條片先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7fxKfzZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fxKfzZ.png&h=e293ece2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/B_5KyuzgEFu/?igshid=493kxa5lqbeu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FB_5KyuzgEFu%2F%3Figshid%3D493kxa5lqbeu&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0CWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=38d544d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/B_5KyuzgEFu/?igshid=493kxa5lqbeu</a><br />\n<br />\n大家一直以嚟既努力 一直堅守既黃色經濟圈 <br />\n平時成日講好嬲好嬲 可以做啲咩<br />\n<br />\n今日 大家有件事係一定要做 <br />\n無做到既話 其實上面講過既野你同無做過無分別<br />\n<br />\n因為假如今日郭榮鏗失守咗 之後既野都會兵敗如山倒<br />\n<br />\n今日 一定要睇住立法會發生啲咩事 支持郭榮鏗 支持民主派"},{"pid":"e265bd263988a9ea81bdb58796535ffcef2b1e02","tid":2006584,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T01:19:18.000Z","msg":"6:00pm<br />\n<br />\n民主派記招<br />\n<br />\n今日係民主最黑暗一日！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2c9fbc39139107bb61b3bc6162363a822a156e","tid":2006584,"uid":55456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T01:20:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467c8c6a403d1d8cb87a115dbb53cf82c4449e9c","tid":2006584,"uid":83910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"泛民邊個今日表現好既<br />\n立法會選舉優先投佢"},{"pid":"073ebe75d8757f3c36ff190836b19779a1a528e9","tid":2006584,"uid":247305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T01:21:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5